1990;;Hamlet;;British;;Franco Zeffirelli;;Mel Gibson, Glenn Close;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hamlet_(1990_film);;In Denmark, Prince Hamlet finds himself involved in a conspiracy of power to the royal palace. Cruel uncle Claudius kills his brother and takes the power of the kingdom. After an encounter with the restless ghost of his murdered father, Hamlet feigns madness and plots to take vengeance.